    "prism_workshop_level": {
      "title": "Prism Workshop Level",
      "text": "The maintenance stairs lead to a working level where crystal artisans shape prisms and mirrors. The workshops hum with activity as light is bent, focused, and redirected through an intricate network of optical devices.\n\nSeveral passages lead from here to different parts of the Cartel's operations and beyond.",
